    "## 11. Conclusion\n",
    "<a id='11-conclusion'></a>\n",
    "\n",
    "### ✅ What We Built\n",
    "| Component | Description |\n",
    "|-----------|-------------|\n",
    "| **ALS Model** | Collaborative filtering on user-product rating matrix using PySpark MLlib |\n",
    "| **Cross-Validation** | Hyperparameter tuning over rank and regularization |\n",
    "| **Neo4j Graph** | Nodes: User, Product, Category, Brand; Edges: RATED, BELONGS_TO, MADE_BY |\n",
