    "- ALS is a scalable, high-quality collaborative filtering approach for large sparse matrices\n",
    "- Neo4j excels at traversing relationships (similar users, product clusters) in real-time\n",
    "- A hybrid approach combines both signals for better diversity and accuracy\n",
    "\n",
